Hi  Kevin,
Stop beating that wiper motor up and install a voltage drop.
    If you are running a 1965 only motor with self parking system, the over
voltage will spin the motor so fast as to skip past the contact gap in it that
is supposed to stop the motor in the correct position.

 E&B
